<title>USA: Box Energy names Smith Barney adviser.</title>
<headline>Box Energy names Smith Barney adviser.</headline>
<dateline>DALLAS 1997-05-08</dateline>
<text>
<p>Box Energy Corp said on Thursday that it has retained Smith Barney as exclusive financial adviser for a review of the company's strategic alternatives.</p>
<p>The company said it is cutting costs, progressing to put litigation behind it, and is planning capital investments in exploration, exploitation and acquisition activities.</p>
<p>On April 22, the company said it was seeking acquisitions with the focus being on properties in the Gulf Coast.</p>
